column2: "Iyinom nye Israelmba akwantu a wɔnam Moses nye Aaron nsa do fi Egypt asaase do tutui dɛ mbrɛ hɔn dɔm tsetsee."
"Na Moses nam EWURADZE mbrasɛm do kyerɛɛw hɔn edzifir dɛ mbrɛ hɔn akwantu mu asoɛe no tse: na iyinom nye hɔn akwantu mu asoɛe dɛ mbrɛ hɔn edzifir tse."
"Na bosoom a odzi kan no mu wotui fii Rameses
column3: wɔ bosoom a odzi kan no mu da a otsia duenum no; apaho no ekyir adzekyee na Israelmba no dze ahosɛpɛw kɛse fiir edzi wɔ Egyptfo nyinara enyim
column5: "wɔ aber a Egyptfo risie sie hɔn mbakan nyinara a EWURADZE kunkum hɔn wɔ hɔn mu no: na hɔn enyame no so EWURADZE buu hɔn ntsɛn."

column2: "Na Israelmba no tui fii Rameses na wɔkɛkyeer nsera wɔ Sukɔt."

column3: na wɔkɛkyeer nsera wɔ Etam a ɔwɔ sar no ano no."
na wɔdanee baa Pi-hahirot a ɔwɔ Baal-zefon enyim no bio: na wɔkyeer nsera wɔ Migidɔl enyim."
na wokotwaa mu faa po no ne finimfin kɔr sar no do: na wɔnantseew ndaansa kwan wɔ Etam sar no do
na wɔbaa Elim: na Elim hɔ na nsunyiwa duebien
column4: nye nkyiresua ndua eduosuon wɔ; na wɔkyeer hɔ nsera."

column3: na wɔkɛkyeer nsera wɔ Mbɛw Po a binom frɛ no Po kɔkɔɔ no ho."

column2: "Na wotui fii Mbɛw Po no ho
column3: na wɔkɛkyeer nsera wɔ Sin sar do."

column4: mbrɛ ɔman no ennya nsu annom no a."

column3: na wɔkɛkyeer nsera wɔ Sinai sar do."
na wɔkɛkyeer nsera wɔ bepɔw Sefer do."

column2: "Na wotui fii Makhelot na wɔkɛkyeer nsera wɔ Tahat."
"Na wotui fii Mitka na wɔkɛkyeer nsera wɔ Hasmona."
"Na wotui fii Hasmona na wɔkɛkyeer nsera wɔ Maserot."

column3: na wɔkɛkyeer nsera wɔ Zin sar do (ɔnoara nye Kades)."
na wɔkɛkyeer nsera wɔ bepɔw Hor do

column2: "Na ɔsɔfo Aaron nam EWURADZE mbrasɛm do fowee kɔr bepɔw Hor do na okowui wɔ hɔ
column3: wɔ afe a Israelmba fi Egypt asaase do firii no ekyir dza otsia eduanan no mu
column4: bosoom a otsia enum no mu da a odzi bosoom no ne kan no."

column2: "Na aber a Aaron wui wɔ bepɔw Hor do no na oedzi mfe ɔha eduonu ebiasa."

column3: Aradhen no a ɔtse Keenan asaase do wɔ Pomu afamu no tsee dɛ Israelmba no reba."
na wɔkɛkyeer nsera wɔ Abarim mbepɔw do
na wɔkɛkyeer nsera wɔ Moab tɛtɛr mu
fi Bɛt-jesimot araa kodur Abel-Sittim wɔ Moab tɛtɛr mu."

column2: "Na EWURADZE kasaa kyerɛɛ Moses wɔ Moab tɛtɛr mu wɔ Jeriko Jordan ho
column7: Sɛ hom twa Jordan kɔ Keenan asaase do a
column9: "ɔno hom mpam asaase no do atsefo no nyinara mfi hom enyim
column10: na hom nsɛɛ hɔn abo ehonyi nyinara
column11: na hom nsɛɛ hɔn ehonyi a woegu no nyinara
column12: na hom ndwurudwuruw mbea sorɔnsorɔm nyinara:"

column3: na hom ntsena do: na hom na medze asaase no ama hom dɛ hom mfa."

column2: "Na hom ntwe tonto mfa nkyɛ asaase no dɛ mbrɛ hom ebusua ebusua tsetsee; hɔn a wɔso no hom mma hɔn egyapadze a ɔso
column3: na hɔn a wosuar no ma hɔn egyapadze a osuar: beebiara mbrɛ tonto no abɔ nyimpa biara no hɔ na ɔnyɛ nedze; dɛ mbrɛ hom egyanom mbusuakuw tsetsee no na hom nyinya hom egyapadze."

column2: "Na sɛ hom ammpam asaase no do atsefo no wɔ hom enyim a; ɔno hɔn mu hɔn a hom ama wɔaka no bɛyɛ dɛ awowɔdze wɔ hom enyiwa mu
column5: na woehiahia hom ho wɔ asaase a hom tse do no do."

column3: dɛ mbrɛ modween dɛ mebɛyɛ hɔn no
